<div class="c-order-section">
    <h2 class="c-order-section__title c-title c-title--3">Оплата</h2>

    <div class="f-layout">
        <div class="f-layout__item f-layout__item--1/6">
            <div class="f-checkblock">
                <input id="orderPayment1" name="orderPayment" type="radio" class="f-checkblock-input">
                <label for="orderPayment1" class="f-checkblock-label">
                    <div class="f-checkblock-label__img">
                        <img src="../img/svg/a-pay.svg" alt="Apple Pay" width="60" height="24">
                    </div>
                </label>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="f-layout__item f-layout__item--1/6">
            <div class="f-checkblock">
                <input id="orderPayment2" name="orderPayment" type="radio" class="f-checkblock-input">
                <label for="orderPayment2" class="f-checkblock-label">
                    <div class="f-checkblock-label__img">
                        <img src="../img/svg/g-pay.svg" alt="Google Pay" width="60" height="24">
                    </div>
                </label>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="f-layout__item f-layout__item--1/3">
            <div class="f-checkblock">
                <input id="orderPayment3" name="orderPayment" type="radio" class="f-checkblock-input">
                <label for="orderPayment3" class="f-checkblock-label">
                    <div class="f-checkblock-label__title">Банківська картка</div>
                </label>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="f-layout__item f-layout__item--1/3">
            <div class="f-checkblock">
                <input id="orderPayment4" checked name="orderPayment" type="radio" class="f-checkblock-input">
                <label for="orderPayment4" class="f-checkblock-label">
                    <div class="f-checkblock-label__title">Оплата при отриманні</div>
                </label>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="c-order-section is-disabled">
    <h2 class="c-order-section__title c-title c-title--3">Оплата</h2>

    <div class="c-order-alert">Для вибору способу оплати спершу необхідно вибрати спосіб доставки</div>
</div>
